@startuml session_schema
title session_state — Table Schema

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam classAttributeFontSize 12

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  BorderColor #444444
  HeaderBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
  FontStyle bold
}

class session_state <<(T,#4488CC) table>> {
  .. **Primary Key** ..
  🔑 session_token : String (PK)
  .. **Core Banking context (server-side only)** ..
  jwt : String [NOT NULL]
  account_id : Integer [NOT NULL]
  account_number : String [NOT NULL]
  .. **Cached for ATM responses** ..
  balance : Float [NOT NULL]
  customer_name : String [NOT NULL]
  .. **TTL / idle tracking** ..
  last_active : DateTime(tz) [NOT NULL]
  created_at : DateTime(tz) [NOT NULL]
}

note right of session_state
  **Token generation:**
  secrets.token_hex(32) at login

  **ATM sends:** X-Session-Token header
  **ATM never receives:** jwt (stays in DB)

  **Idle expiry:**
  SESSION_TTL_SECONDS = 900 (15 min)
  last_active refreshed on get() and touch()

  **Background cleanup:**
  _session_cleanup thread every 60s
  deletes rows where last_active < cutoff
end note

note bottom of session_state
  **NOT stored:** PIN, password, credentials
  **No foreign keys** — self-contained operational table

  **balance** is a cache updated via
  update_balance() after deposit/withdraw;
  Core Banking remains source of truth.
end note

@enduml
